{"title":"3. Trastornos del páncreas","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/MKSAP - 18/Gastroenterología/3. Trastornos del páncreas.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Trastornos del\\Npáncreas","guid":"zrTTVyfks8Y_shSouCmkuQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Pancreatitis\\Naguda","guid":"ej6uErIKtZBOqa-xLdVXbw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"General ","guid":"h7HRqBpPtCXaKLTOn1rkLA","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"proceso inflamatorio que afecta al páncreas y a órganos extrapancreáticos","guid":"FhtocXYLWNEMPyOkvczAuw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"causa gastrointestinal de hospitalización más frecuente","guid":"YVkzIEoJN7he-XAnKLJbpA","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"activación prematura de las enzimas digestivas y la liberación de\\Ncitocinas provocan «autodigestión» del páncreas e inflamación","guid":"sos1LOqP-WBakKUQf6joHg","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"pueden afectar a los tejidos\\Ncircundantes y a órganos distantes","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"causa","guid":"YJcTAJwRCnVYBzMbErUALA","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"cálculos biliares, barro o\\Ncristales biliares (microlitiasis)","guid":"uwyljM9SLWDn3bi7ONblug","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"causa más frecuente","guid":"UqO0BMAc3SLisk9WJ7PqEQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"clasifica","guid":"SQ9y4MykFNJ6lrgpYDFRjg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"leve","guid":"LgXUgDrg9GFgoHt9SYUN3A","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"no produce insuficiencia orgánica ni complicaciones locales o sistémicas","guid":"dgQwAPhFFRovTBHkfPg4pw","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"normalmente se resuelve en una semana y tiene una tasa de mortalidad baja","guid":"78YJ6rcDZStnVLwTK24Etg","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"20%","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"moderadamente grave","guid":"VP8Q6MxrRi20wPy__eSx1A","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"complicaciones sistémicas como necrosis o insuficiencia\\Norgánica transitoria (durante menos de 48 horas)","guid":"JsQGFPyzsil6tgW04iZU0A","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"grave","guid":"MXdsV5UBBiTFpd7m5rEMqw","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"síndrome de respuesta inflamatoria sistémica (SRIS), insuficiencia orgánica persistente (normalmente\\Ninsuficiencia renal o respiratoria), tiempo de evolución superior a 48 horas y una o varias complicaciones locales","guid":"GkRRtbK9Gr3Wqj6Fbov4_w","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"mortalidad 50%","guid":"d6ISuzfQ86b16SGB5UlR1w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"1","text":"Presentación clínica\\Ny diagnóstico","guid":"EkTsnjFsvlORLtiFEeNaJQ","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Diagnóstico \\Ndos de los tres criterios","guid":"_vBfHs-rqQLPCpLk-P7KAA","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"1) dolor abdominal de aparición aguda\\Ncaracterístico de la pancreatitis","guid":"fh4iBYkLMnDNoq4MoWjNZA","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"intenso, persistente durante horas o días y situado en el\\Nepigastrio, a menudo con irradiación a la espalda","guid":"fYMprAeIix2DKFC5UIy77w","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"2) niveles séricos de lipasa o amilasa elevados entre tres y\\Ncinco veces el límite superior de la normalidad","guid":"xlzrAPBF9HxMlTJVXBtREQ","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"3) hallazgos radiográficos característicos","guid":"z2H1KPoMXENVFGKt_fPnBw","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"TC con contraste","guid":"Zo1HxWko-4p_YaKrkmoDSQ","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"resonancia magnética (RM)","guid":"1UuoU3IiQoqCHEJzTfx6rA","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"ecografía transabdominal","guid":"JBRVSk-W0H78zJ4lqeBRYQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"20","text":"Estudio ","guid":"1jDOkO9b7osgiRXxEjDxMw","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Imágenes ","guid":"3vKtC3km9lr_3H3a9vSGBA","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"ecografía\\Ntransabdominal","guid":"yqU1ruZ7_zz14vuNzhWw2w","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"mayor sensibilidad para la detección de cálcu los biliares","guid":"sE0sBatkuxS8AASOK9RVBg","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"aire abdominal puede limitar la visualización del páncreas","guid":"smruIj1ruZgHO5zkx8Twyw","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"colangiopancreatografía por\\Nresonancia magnética (CPRM)","guid":"Gp7VkiqZ3KgBNySC1CF9Sg","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"En los pacientes sin hallazgos anómalos en la ecografía","guid":"4jW-TBWVPdX7NZEi9AwUoA","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"30","text":"TC\\NIndicada en","guid":"TZKHKiHshA4oTZRKK7fYYA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"duda diagnóstica","guid":"vW72-1R4-A98Z3IOND98-g","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"ausencia de alivio de los\\Nsíntomas clínicos en las 48 primeras horas","guid":"TqXyzAeujv09_Suww0oj6Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"29","text":"Laboratorio ","guid":"NEUXB8u4GvAKQV6FZpPm3w","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"elevación aguda de las enzimas hepáticas en la\\Npresentación es indicativa de obstrucción biliar","guid":"lxd5AtOk7M4OcAVXcDl__g","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"niveles séricos de\\Namilasa y lipasa","guid":"HAMAeOnNVCZEHJpr1yMMXA","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"pueden estar elevados en trastornos\\Ndistintos de la pancreatitis aguda","guid":"XyxHpRgqJ2STLL9LNoeLKg","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"enfermedad renal, la apendicitis aguda, la colecistitis, la obstrucción\\Nintestinal o la isquemia, la úlcera péptica o trastornos ginecológicos","guid":"yycMI7-X_fFnZaBJKyrFrg","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"falsamente bajos\\No normales","guid":"ytgkqzgLl3e0D3OYRcaNvg","ch