o y una\\Nexactitud limitados","guid":"D42EkqUlm_8iQ6VoDyWnNg","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"identifican la enfermedad grave cuando aparece, no dejan plazo suficiente\\Npara la intervención y son demasiado complicados para su uso rutinario","guid":"sTmrCF-tzmLrIty9hZN0BA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"1","text":"Manejo","guid":"LLKo_CY4q-BWVvMrkSdLWw","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"▶️","guid":"7BJoiDyBWk-L5dGVcuMg-w","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"hidratación\\Nagresiva","guid":"MrzrtVhf6bLu36YLywT-vQ","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"250-500 ml/h de solución de Ringer lactada intravenosa","guid":"9qwbbKH1W6oNT8dfLGpVIA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"especialmente beneficiosa en las primeras 12-24 horas","guid":"jrXov-JTM6X9cYWl8sM4Aw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"disminución del volumen grave puede ser necesaria\\Nuna reanimación con líquidos más rápida (bolos)","guid":"1-4_6TEGJe8JNfXvZVTCXQ","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"insuficiencia\\Norgánica o SRIS","guid":"wvRLcIgbKOwL0fq-m5TBHw","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"UCI","guid":"2XJtD5-dgPQvB8g_ZS9q_g","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"reevaluación de las necesidades de líquidos cada\\Nseis horas a partir de las 24 o 48 primeras horas.","guid":"WH3_2p0_rDQ8wuNbtTrIxA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"63","text":"control del dolor","guid":"oqTePPGk1cab7Hkmg7JaKA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"63","text":"administración de medicamentos\\Ncontra las náuseas","guid":"iZQuVmuERmg_Tpdrx2sogg","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"62","text":"antibióticos","guid":"j0zqmX-ArIEhs-yUqwcUMg","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"uso rutinario no está justificado","guid":"GQtbMQS46v36FH6KqEHEHw","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"Indicación ante pruebas de\\Ninfección extrapancreática","guid":"HSV_FRy2R_Jqps3dJ3EQhg","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"colangitis ascendente, bacteriemia,\\Ninfección urinaria o neumonía","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"62","text":"Alimentación ","guid":"GjL36o_cIQJxkis4y4fRhg","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"pancreatitis\\Naguda leve","guid":"__VeLAVvPa3r1SdGFxB8Uw","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"oral","guid":"0E6Q31RicFSVLZT1n_MVWA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"iniciarse en cuanto las náuseas y los vómitos estén\\Ncontrolados y los síntomas clínicos empiecen a remitir","guid":"LYvzaGWVRxH8ilVBTsLOcg","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"77","text":"pancreatitis aguda\\Nmoderadamente grave o grave","guid":"VjaOFWJ8o-K4d8KUQBKIVQ","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"iniciarse una alimentación\\Nenteral en el plazo de 72 horas","guid":"A97EPIg-Xa3VJ7gCRlRL6w","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"sonda nasoyeyunal, nasogástrica es igualmente\\Neficaz y más fácil de administrar","guid":"7JBvt93kXYuSjK2O9nKaGg","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"favorece una barrera mucosa intestinal sana para prevenir\\Nla traslocación de bacterias a los tejidos inflamados","guid":"p4T13TDQRJSQLKnAB2Zn-Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"62","text":"presunta\\Ncausa biliar","guid":"-AyHttb2SkFwr5bhQxacig","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"analíticas bioquímicas\\Nhepáticas seriadas","guid":"Emdx3Un8uiC-0siPSdNtrQ","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"revelar si la obstrucción biliar está en\\Ncurso o en vías de resolución","guid":"c4YFG0ax64vi5hUfw2veGQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"colangiopancreatografía\\Nretrógrada endoscópica (CPRE)","guid":"-RshptTBxlhugVBiCAg96g","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"elevación persistente de los parámetros bioquímicos hepáticos\\No que se observe coledocolitiasis en las pruebas de imagen","guid":"xSsBagJyxrnvz4RTmdt2eA","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"colecistectomía antes del alta","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"62","text":"pacientes con colangitis","guid":"olhsIKg4LxHQxWl9B1xTTw","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"CPRE en las 24 horas posteriores al ingreso","guid":"ZrorEfXMX9MEdont40ucpQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"62","text":"No es útil volver a comprobar los niveles de amilasa y lipasa una vez emitido el diagnóstico","guid":"xT0GAf2x5X8fOnLsPajwlA","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"1","text":"Complicaciones","guid":"osu8hU4FsNC-dTil3I6hdg","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"fase inicial","guid":"kurbzCA0UNF4r-_FH_V68w","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"primera semana de la enfermedad","guid":"jpU95VjNXL6HXaYw89bI0g","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"organismo responde a la lesión pancreática local y la cascada\\Nde citocinas y pueden darse SRIS e insuficiencia orgánica","guid":"6JtJsjdQLjAkIg79Vn8KLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"94","text":"fase tardía ","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"después de la primera semana y puede persistir semanas o meses en\\Nlos pacientes con pancreatitis aguda moderadamente grave o grave","guid":"0kMYAVN8RT4t0klQRdRALA","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"riesgo significativo de infección en las colecciones\\Nde líquido peripancreáticas y necrosis","guid":"icPOua9vb2-ioTffP-difQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"94","text":"clasificación de Atlanta\\Ntipo colecciones de líquido","guid":"2WDNorhBkdqx1MWM0PEWfw","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"colecciones líquidas\\Nperipancreáticas agudas","guid":"FfJtXYxh23Fi4PG433q7gA","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"pancreatitis intersticial edematosa (sin necrosis) en las cuatro primeras semana","guid":"rOmJdH5yyjRNiqid6XeKkg","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"cree que se deben a la rotura de numerosas ramas laterales de los conductos","guid":"3PDKwCETlgfW3ZhuUrcQsg","children":[]},{"id":"105","paren