istes","guid":"EfjW2ndOytOBALB0PIftcQ","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"281","text":"citología del líquido del quiste tiene una\\Nsensibilidad baja (<60%)","guid":"_QdORZO_cM4ZwWQaQQNHeA","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"no constituye un predictor fiable\\Nde transformación maligna","guid":"mg5-BGJNlpDUEAGro8wOOQ","children":[]}]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"286","parent":"264","text":"No productores de mucina","guid":"ByGcVD_Zp120OXetIqg5bQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"261","text":"Tratamiento ","guid":"1vYRgh0PSe4JLORmNDe-mg","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"resección quirúrgica es la única opción terapéutica para los quistes de alto riesgo","guid":"Sinhj2-4IgzbXOVCKzvkhw","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"287","text":"alto riesgo","guid":"IwUcqIYiXEkQYse6eb0Y5Q","children":[{"id":"290","parent":"289","text":"síntomas relacionados con el quiste (ictericia, pancreatitis), un tamaño ≥3 cm,\\Nla dilatación del conducto pancreático principal y un componente sólido","guid":"BvXfiAUUq7CsKOy6oyqXsA","children":[]}]},{"id":"291","parent":"287","text":"Seguimiento\\Ncon RNM","guid":"u8zNVLTQAvF1v1WXVh99Pw","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"pueden interrumpirse si no se observan signos\\Npreocupantes en cinco años o si el paciente deja\\Nde ser candidato a cirugía","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"293","parent":"0","text":"Tumores neuroendocrinos\\Npancreáticos","guid":"KjcscXhZTfYq1pc4XzKyDw","children":[{"id":"294","parent":"293","text":"General ","guid":"ha99CBWZFjQBRUDsi4dcsQ","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"raros","guid":"TgF_Z9XeOVQXAEAt25LkWw","children":[{"id":"296","parent":"295","text":"3% de las neoplasias pancreáticas primarias","guid":"2l1JS_lr8eTIl1eT_3sf0w","children":[]}]},{"id":"297","parent":"294","text":"10% y el 25% de los tumores neuroendocrinos pancreáticos\\Nson funcionales e hipersecretan hormonas","guid":"NaZii4f8TIVnawiRUiBGdg","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"294","text":"pueden